===Etymology===
From Old English [[tun|tūn]]. Cognate with Dutch [[tuin]] ‘garden’, German [[Zaun]], Swedish [[tun]] ‘fence’.

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/taʊn/}}, {{SAMPA|/taUn/}}
